Dennis Bell sraral hya'ga sisyow na NBA, wal malaxmisoq qaniy la. kawas te 1951, byacing te 6 ro 2 ryax qo hintgan nya, kinholan nya ga Ohio, hiya ga mnanak na ppzoy mari waya, ro sqoliq ka ppkal mari waya. 196 konbon kinwagiq nya, 84 konkin kin'sow nya, hiya ga qotox nqo spzyang blaq na ppzoy mari NBA. kawas 1973 mnwayaw ppzoy mari ga, mzyop sqo te qotox lahoy ro te magal sqoliq, galon nqo ew York Knicks. cinkholan sa knita' sa brbiro' Lists of National Basketball Association players == qnxan hetay nya ==
